data.description: Open House Sunday February 25th from 12-3 PM!! This 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence is a perfect blend of modern comfort and timeless charm. As you step through the front door, you'll be greeted by an inviting open floor plan that seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere for family gatherings and entertaining guests. The well-appointed kitchen boasts granite countertops, modern appliances, and ample cabinet space, making meal preparation a breeze. The spacious primary bedroom offers a tranquil retreat with an ensuite bathroom that features dual vanities, garden tub and a standup walk-in shower. Three additional bedrooms and full bath ensure plenty of space for family members or guests. One of the standout features of this home is the meticulously maintained outdoor space. A lush green lawn is complemented by a state-of-the-art sprinkler system, ensuring your yard stays vibrant year-round with minimal effort. The added convenience of a water softener adds to the luxury, providing you with the finest quality water for your daily needs. Conveniently located in Converse City, you'll enjoy easy access to nearby parks, schools, and shopping centers. This home is not just a property; it's a lifestyle. Don't miss the opportunity to make this stunning residence your own. Schedule a showing today and experience the comfort and elegance that awaits you in this charming Texas home!
